# Pull Request

## Description

Please include a summary of the changes. If this pull request is linked to an issue,
include the issue being fixed. If this pull request adds notes for a paper reading,
include the title of the paper and briefly justify why this paper is relevant (i.e.
topic).

## Type of Change

- [ ] New Paper Notes
- [ ] Modify Existing Notes
- [ ] Organization
- [ ] Other (Explain)

## Checklist

- [ ] My notes follow the provided template in the README.
- [ ] My notes have been checked for grammatical errors and are
      generally coherent and readable.
- [ ] I have added the paper to the Zotero group `swamp rats`.
